      <title>瑞士信贷投资组合经理辞职成立新宏观基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/credit-suisse-portfolio-managers-resign-to-set-up-new-macro-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，瑞士信贷的五名投资组合经理将离开该行，在 Lombard Odier Investment Managers 的另类投资平台上设立一支新的全球宏观基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/credit-suisse-portfolio-managers-resign-to-set-up-new-macro-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 08:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
